## Authentication Flow Issues
- 401 errors on /api/v1/groups/my-groups indicate JWT token is not being sent or is invalid
- Token is stored in localStorage with key 'nexus_token' by both authStore.ts and api/client.ts
- The auth flow: Telegram initData -> /auth/token -> JWT token -> localStorage -> API requests with Bearer token
- If JWT_SECRET changes between token creation and validation, tokens will be invalid
